    <h1>What is FnordMetric?</h1>
    <p>
      FnordMetric consists of two components: a query engine that executes a
      superset of standard SQL against a number of backends and a C++ library
      that renders SVG charts from plain old data. While you could use each of
      these components on its own, awesomness ensues when you mash them together.
      Think peanut butter and jelly.
    </p>
